results.description:
Angular2 is slowly shaping-up and it is in alpha stage and time to explore new syntax and everything about it.

Here is what we will talk \ present:
1) What is AngularJS 2.0 all about? Why a rewrite is needed?
2) What are the challenges?
3) Change Detection
4) Dependency Injection
5) Templating
6) What is ShadowDOM?
7) Routing
8) Documentation
9) Benchmarking
10) Hello Angular2 example and syntax changes
11) IDE support (Web Storm, Visual Studio, Sublime, Atom, Brackets etc)

** You can RSVP now but we will have questioner and re-confirmation 1 or 2 days before the meetup because of 50-60% no show-ups. I hope you understand why we need to do this.
results.name: Angular-2 Intro
